OL,3,CWhat is Labour's huge shake-up of
OL,4,Clocal government all about?
OL,6,FWhy is the Government embarking on the
OL,7,Fbiggest shake-up of local government
OL,8,Fin a generation - and will it be worth
OL,9,Fit? This policy - to abolish dozens of
OL,10,Fcouncils and create larger ones in
OL,11,Ftheir place - has not received as much
OL,12,Fattention as it might, because it is
OL,13,Fsomewhat complicated and occasionally
OL,14,Ftechnical.
OL,16,FBut it does represent an enormous
OL,17,Fshift in the shape and structure of
OL,18,Fcouncils across England. And that
OL,19,Fmakes it highly controversial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
