OL,3,CWhat is Labour's huge shake-up of
OL,4,Clocal government all about?
OL,6,FOn Friday, the County Councils Network
OL,7,Fpublished a report saying that this
OL,8,Fradical policy could save the
OL,9,Fgovernment billions of pounds to
OL,10,Finvest in public services.
OL,12,FHowever, the previous day, a survey
OL,13,Ffrom the Local Government Information
OL,14,FUnit cited figures in town halls
OL,15,Fsaying the plans to merge councils are
OL,16,F"ill thought out", "insane" and
OL,17,F"bizarre".
OL,19,FSo what is going on?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
