OL,3,CWhat is Labour's huge shake-up of
OL,4,Clocal government all about?
OL,6,FThese proposals largely affect the 21
OL,7,Fareas in the country where we have two-
OL,8,Ftier local government.
OL,10,FThese areas have one umbrella
OL,11,Forganisation, a vast county council
OL,12,F(upper tier), that is responsible for
OL,13,Fadult and children's social care.
OL,15,FBelow that, in the lower tier, are
OL,16,Fseveral district or borough councils,
OL,17,Fcovering a much smaller area for which
OL,18,Fthey are responsible for services like
OL,19,Fbin collections and housing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
