OL,3,CWhat is Labour's huge shake-up of
OL,4,Clocal government all about?
OL,6,FThe aim is to effectively roll
OL,7,Ftogether all those councils and
OL,8,Fcreate, in their place, a series of
OL,9,F"unitary" councils that provide all
OL,10,Fthe services for the population in
OL,11,Ftheir locality.
OL,13,FThe argument is that this simplifies
OL,14,Fthings for residents, who will feel
OL,15,Fmore locally linked to a single
OL,16,Forganisation and know that it provides
OL,17,Fall their local services.
OL,19,FBut, really, sources made clear to me
OL,20,Fthat another central aim was to save
OL,21,Fmoney.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
