OL,3,CWhat is Labour's huge shake-up of
OL,4,Clocal government all about?
OL,6,FIn the original white paper for
OL,7,Fdevolution, they cited a PWC report
OL,8,Fthat claimed there could be savings of
OL,9,F#2.9bn.
OL,11,FOne reason for said savings is simple
OL,12,F- if you no longer have multiple
OL,13,Fcouncil chief executives (or a series
OL,14,Fof other senior roles) then you reduce
OL,15,Fyour salary bill a lot.
OL,17,FWhich sounds like a big solution for
OL,18,Flocal councils facing financial crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
