OL,3,CWhat is Labour's huge shake-up of
OL,4,Clocal government all about?
OL,6,FBut here is the thing: that figure was
OL,7,Fcalculated on the basis of each two-
OL,8,Ftier council replacing multiple
OL,9,Fcouncils with a single unitary body.
OL,11,FWhich means the number is wildly
OL,12,Finflated, compared to what will happen
OL,13,Fin reality. Many of these county areas
OL,14,Fare too large to have a single council
OL,15,Freplacing what may be 13 or 14
OL,16,Fdifferent organisations at the moment.
OL,18,FInstead, there will could be two or
OL,19,Fthree per area - or perhaps more. The
OL,20,FGovernment talked about unitaries
OL,21,Fcatering for populations of 500,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
