OL,3,CWhat is Labour's huge shake-up of
OL,4,Clocal government all about?
OL,6,FAccording to Friday's CCN report,
OL,7,Fcreating new councils representing
OL,8,F500,000 people would still save money.
OL,9,FNot as much as that original figure -
OL,10,Fbut #1.8bn over 5 years.
