OL,3,CWhat is Labour's huge shake-up of
OL,4,Clocal government all about?
OL,6,FSources in government insist that
OL,7,Fmoney saving is not the only
OL,8,Fmotivation. They say this is about
OL,9,Fsimpler structures, clearer
OL,10,Faccountability, and targeting
OL,11,Fresources for deprivation.
OL,13,FBut they also know it would be tough
OL,14,Fto justify if a shake up this big to
OL,15,Fend up costing the government - at a
OL,16,Ftime that councils are already in
OL,17,Ffinancial crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
