OL,3,CWhat is Labour's huge shake-up of
OL,4,Clocal government all about?
OL,6,FA Ministry of Housing, Communities and
OL,7,FLocal Government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Due to the inheritance we have been
OL,9,Fleft with, we must reform a crumbling
OL,10,Fsystem unfit for purpose.
OL,12,F"We're working with councils on
OL,13,Fambitious plans to reorganise local
OL,14,Fgovernment. This will deliver much
OL,15,Fneeded long-term and lasting reform
OL,16,Fthat will help give them the stability
OL,17,Fthey need, so they can deliver better
OL,18,Fvalue for money services for
OL,19,Fresidents."
